    {
        "content": "<p>A related trivial lemma that also seems to be missing from the API:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">Ω</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hΩ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hΩ'</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MeasurableSpace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ω</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hΩ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≤</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hΩ'</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ω</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hE</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">@</span><span class=\"n\">MeasurableSet</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ω</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hΩ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">@</span><span class=\"n\">MeasurableSet</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ω</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hΩ'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hE</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
